From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 13:40:04 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] vendor: drop stray Cargo.lock / .cargo_vcs_info.json from
 uutils crates

These are build/package-metadata artifacts (the Cargo.lock was regenerated by
the porting agents' cargo build in /tmp and copied in; .cargo_vcs_info.json is
cargo-package metadata). Neither is part of the uu_cat vendored selection, a
path-dep's own Cargo.lock is ignored (the workspace engine/Cargo.lock is
authoritative), and they bloat the patch diffs. Remove them so every vendored
uutils crate matches the uu_cat convention (src + Cargo.toml(.orig) + LICENSE +
README + locales/benches only).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>

Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01TNBGBV51j5AH4j8k8ENi1W
---
 .cargo_vcs_info.json |   6 -
 Cargo.lock           | 859 -------------------------------------------
 2 files changed, 865 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 engine/vendor/uu_expr/.cargo_vcs_info.json
 delete mode 100644 engine/vendor/uu_expr/Cargo.lock

diff --git a/.cargo_vcs_info.json b/.cargo_vcs_info.json
deleted file mode 100644
index abbd56e..0000000
--- a/.cargo_vcs_info.json
+++ /dev/null
@@ -1,6 +0,0 @@
-{
-  "git": {
-    "sha1": "c4093734e2ebe2efb7d65e216cd1444664bcf26a"
-  },
-  "path_in_vcs": "src/uu/expr"
-}
\ No newline at end of file
diff --git a/Cargo.lock b/Cargo.lock
deleted file mode 100644
index dad4f38..0000000
--- a/Cargo.lock
+++ /dev/null
@@ -1,859 +0,0 @@
